	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002057_0001"><!--pb/@n='74r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName><settlement type="town">Hamilton</settlement></placeName><date when="1864-09-01">1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi><choice><abbr>Sept</abbr><expan>September</expan></choice>
<lb/>1864</date></p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <choice><abbr><unclear>H</unclear>W</abbr><expan>Horace Waller</expan></choice>
<lb/>I was in the
<lb/><placeName><region>Highlands</region></placeName>so yours
<lb/>of <date when="1864-08-15">15<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date> had time
<lb/>to get seasoned here
<lb/>could you explain
<lb/>to <persName>Thorton</persName> that
<lb/>I had to <add place="below">^</add><add place="above">pay the</add> share of the
<lb/>mission sheep &amp; 
<lb/>goats or the whole
<lb/>£70 - I empowered
<lb/><persName><choice><abbr>S<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi></abbr><expan>Senior</expan></choice> Galdino</persName> to
<lb/>pay my £23
<lb/><persName>Bishop Tozer</persName>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002057_0002"><!--pb/@n='74v'--></pb>
<lb/>refusing to advance
<lb/>the £47 the <choice><abbr>Col.</abbr><expan>Colonel</expan></choice> paid
<lb/>it all on my
<lb/>account - The idea
<lb/>I have picked up
<lb/>is that the society
<lb/>paid £47 to <persName>George
<lb/>Thorton</persName> instead
<lb/>of to me else <persName>Tozer</persName>
<lb/>would surely never
<lb/>have refused -</p>
<lb/><p>I am in the
<lb/><term type="ailment">labour pains</term> with
<lb/>my speech - A cold
<lb/>shiver comes over 
<lb/>me when I think
<lb/>of its delivery</p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002057_0003"><!--pb/@n='75r'--></pb>
<lb/><p><persName>Bishop Colenzo</persName>
<lb/>is reported to <hi rend="underline">be invited</hi>
<lb/>to the <placeName><settlement type="town">Bath</settlement></placeName> Meeting!
<lb/>What Muffs you
<lb/>High Church people
<lb/>are - Why not give
<lb/><persName><unclear>Chimwala</unclear></persName> to
<lb/><persName>Rowley</persName> - He will
<lb/>baptize him no
<lb/>doubt at once</p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002057_0004"><!--pb/@n='75v'--></pb>
			
